    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="借用构造函数实现继承"><a href="#借用构造函数实现继承" class="headerlink" title="借用构造函数实现继承"></a>借用构造函数实现继承</h2><blockquote>
<ul>
<li>思路: 在子类构造函数中调用父类构造函数,通过使用call和apply方法在新创建对象上执行构造函数;<ul>
<li>缺点: 方法都在构造函数中定义,函数的复用无从谈起,父类构造函数中的方法对子类构造函数而言是不可见的,结果<br>   所有类型都只能使用构造函数模式</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;html lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;head&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot; /&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;title&gt;Document&lt;/title&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/head&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;body&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;script&gt;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        function SuperType()&#123;</div><div class="line">            this.color = [&apos;red&apos;,&apos;green&apos;,&apos;blue&apos;];</div><div class="line">            //缺点: 方法都在构造函数中定义,函数的复用无从谈起</div><div class="line">            //父类的构造函数对子类而言是不可见的,结果所有类型都只能使用构造函数模式</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        function SubType()&#123;</div><div class="line">            SuperType.call(this);</div><div class="line">            //在子类构造函数中调用父类构造函数中的方法</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        var instance1 = new SubType();</div><div class="line">        instance1.color.push(&quot;yellow&quot;);</div><div class="line">        alert(instance1.color);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        var instance2 = new SubType();</div><div class="line">        alert(instance2.color)</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    &lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/body&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/html&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
